# Netlify Redirects
# Proxies all /api/* requests to your Render backend.
# This means index.html can use API_BASE = '/api' on both Netlify and Render.
# The browser only ever sees your Netlify domain — no CORS issues.
#
# IMPORTANT: Replace the URL below with your actual Render service URL.

/api/*  https://pollspace.onrender.com/api/:splat  200
